metadata.name: LEAP
metadata.description:
Run, run, run.

The rabbit holds her watch.

"I’m late. I’m late. I’m late."

She runs up to the sky.

I chase after the rabbit.

I rises into the sky.

Up, up, up, up.

I'm going to a new world.




Time is limited.

And life is limited.

We live with limited time, making choices. 

No matter which choice we make It doesn't matter, as long as we choose the right path with the right heart.


Run, run, run

And sometimes

Stop, rest, sleep☆
